%h1 Blue Trolley

%p="Hi #{@user.name},"

%p
  We received a request to reset the password associated with this email address. If you made this request,
  please follow the instructions below.
%p
  if you did not request to have your password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
  %br
  To reset your password click the link below:

= link_to 'Reset Password', edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email)

%p
  This link will expire in two hours.
  %br
  If clicking the link does not work, you can copy and paste the link into your browser's address window,
  or retype it there.

%p
  Thanks,
  %br
  Blue Trolley
